title: Paul Allen Friday Football Feast (5/18)
description: IT'S A FRIDAY FOOTBALL FEAST! PA and Charch get a call from Bud Grant, a visit from Matt Birk in the studio for the Birk Bit, Ron Flatter chats horse racing, Cheryl Reeve checks in, and they wrap up the show with Paul Howard!
